Write a {{durationType}} POV slideshow script for the scenario: "{{title}}"

Voice style: {{voiceStyle}}
Pacing: {{pacing}}

Return JSON with this exact structure:
{
  "title": "string",
  "hook": "Opening line that grabs attention in under 3 seconds",
  "sections": [
    {
      "label": "Morning|Afternoon|Evening|etc",
      "narration": "What the narrator says for this slide",
      "imagePrompt": "Detailed cinematic image prompt for AI generation",
      "durationSeconds": 8
    }
  ],
  "outro": "Closing line with subtle call to action",
  "totalEstimatedDuration": "e.g. 10 minutes",
  "tags": ["tag1", "tag2", "tag3"]
}

Include 8-15 slides depending on duration. Make each image prompt highly visual and specific.
